Name: Allvetica
Author: Lu√≠s Rodrigues
Version: 1.1

Google Chrome extension to replace Arial on every page with the superior Helvetica typeface.

Please note that Helvetica is not packaged with this extension, and you must have it on your computer for correct font replacement.

Arial versus Helvetica:
http://www.ilovetypography.com/2007/10/06/arial-versus-helvetica/

Google Chrome Extension Gallery URL:
https://chrome.google.com/extensions/detail/acgbckcjlpneapibaifnhpjnnakijihm

github Project URL:
http://github.com/goblindegook/Allvetica